&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;\question&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;[1.0]&lt;/span&gt; Section 9.2 Problem 12 &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;\\&lt;/span&gt;
